                        <h1 class="global-hero__title">Digital Community Guidelines</h1>
                        <p class="global-hero__description"><p>Thank you for participating on our first ever digital CES. For the first-time, CES is going worldwide &mdash; audiences from across the globe will be able to experience the latest breakthroughs in technology. This provides us an opportunity to connect with new people and to connect with more people than ever before. With this opportunity also comes a greater responsibility.</p>
